Nestled in the midst of nature and spread over ~5 acres of verdant greens, with a lifestyle at par with the global best, Lodha Woods give you the opportunity to live in a landmark development at Kandivali East, which will change the way you live forever. With 80% open space and over 1 lakh sq. ft. of landscape and recreational spaces, you’ll find life is different out here. There’s a butterfly for every car in the concrete jungle; a bird chirping for every horn blaring; a tree for every traffic signal. Here, your morning alarm is the call of the Koel, and you sleep to the rhythmic chorus of a thousand crickets. With a range of amenities and services to elevate your lifestyle, and a like-minded community you can relate to and bond with, it’s the perfect balance of nature and lifestyle conceived for you. 

At Lodha Woods, you find a range of 30+ amenities that will cater to your every need, and fulfill every desire. Lodha Woods has something for everyone in the family. A quiet corner for the elders, a swimming pool for your little ones, and a special area for your pets to socialize with their own. A Jain temple, meditation and yoga pavilion, allows you to connect with your inner self. Get your little champ Olympic ready – you’ve got a kid’s swimming pool, football turf, volleyball court and a basketball half-court to train him. And for the adults, a cricket ground, 25 mt lap pool, and more. At Lodha Woods, you have every amenity you can think of and a lifestyle you couldn’t even dream of.
